    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Holding power, durability, terrain diversity, as well as easy installation and packability, these lightweight but heavy duty ABS plastic tent stakes from ASR Outdoor boast it all. The tent stakes feature pointed tips, large top stoppers and stringing eyelets for easy and quick installation. Featuring a lightweight but heavy duty design, these tent stakes feature single body ABS plastic construction, increasing ground anchor integrity, durability and longevity, as well as making installation and removal efficient. The purposeful lightweight design and material construction make these tent pegs ideal for camping, backpacking, hiking, mountaineering and more, as they won’t weigh your gear down in comparison to other heavier metal ground anchors.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Orange Heavy Duty ABS Plastic Tent Stakes Ground Anchor (2 Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Holding power, durability, terrain diversity, as well as easy installation and packability, these lightweight but heavy duty ABS plastic tent stakes from ASR Outdoor boast it all.</p>\n  <p>The tent stakes feature pointed tips, large top stoppers and stringing eyelets for easy and quick installation. Featuring a lightweight but heavy duty design, these tent stakes feature single body ABS plastic construction, increasing ground anchor integrity, durability and longevity, as well as making installation and removal efficient. The purposeful lightweight design and material construction make these tent pegs ideal for camping, backpacking, hiking, mountaineering and more, as they won’t weigh your gear down in comparison to other heavier metal ground anchors.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>CAMPING ESSENTIALS:</strong> ASR Outdoor heavy duty tent pegs feature unibody ABS plastic construction, making them a reliable choice to ensure camping tents or other shelter types are firmly secured; the tent stakes feature pointed tips, large stoppers and stringing eyelets for easy and quick installation</li>\n    <li><strong>UNIBODY CONSTRUCTION:</strong> Lightweight but heavy duty, these ABS plastic material tent stakes feature single body construction, increasing the ground anchors integrity, durability and longevity, as well as making installation and removal more efficient</li>\n    <li><strong>MULTIPURPOSE GROUND ANCHOR:</strong> Whether setting up a camping tent, canopy, for landscaping, tarp tie downs or overhead covering for sporting events or other, these heavy duty tent stakes can handle it all; suitable for use in grass, dirt, gravel and sand terrains</li>\n    <li><strong>LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN FOR TRAVEL:</strong> Purposeful lightweight design and material construction make these tent pegs ideal for camping, backpacking, hiking, mountaineering and more, as they won’t weigh your gear down in comparison to heavier metal ground anchors</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Single Stake Weight: 0.14lbs; Color: High Visibility Orange; Sold in packs of: 4, 6, 8, 10 and 20</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/69241/ASRO_ABS_plastic_tent_stakes_parent_scale.jpg\" alt=\"Holding power, durability, terrain diversity, as well as easy installation and packability, these lightweight but heavy duty ABS plastic tent stakes\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> TNT-STAKE</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Orange</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Reliable and robust, these high visibility orange tent stakes can handle everything from multi person camping tents, tarp tie downs, landscaping projects, overhead installations for sporting events and much more; they’re suitable for use in dirt, sand, gravel and grassy terrains, giving you a diverse selection of ground anchoring possibilities. Their intentional high visibility orange colorway makes the tent stakes easy to spot with your camping gear, as well as in low or dim light environments if installation adjustments are needed.</p>\n  <p>Reach for these lightweight and incredibly sturdy tent stakes from ASR Outdoor come your next camping trip or backcountry adventure!</p>\n  <p>Sold in packs of: 4, 6, 8, 10 and 20</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Holding power, durability, terrain diversity, as well as easy installation and packability, these lightweight but heavy duty ABS plastic tent stakes from ASR Outdoor boast it all. The tent stakes feature pointed tips, large top stoppers and stringing eyelets for easy and quick installation. Featuring a lightweight but heavy duty design, these tent stakes feature single body ABS plastic construction, increasing ground anchor integrity, durability and longevity, as well as making installation and removal efficient. The purposeful lightweight design and material construction make these tent pegs ideal for camping, backpacking, hiking, mountaineering and more, as they won’t weigh your gear down in comparison to other heavier metal ground anchors.",
